column2: Note: The data supplied here are estimates produced from the research of Leo Krippner.
Please refer to my website LJKmfa.com for documentation.
(1) The history of these estimates has changed from the May 2020 update. See the documention
on the ljkmfa.com website for details.
(2) The monthly averages are calculated from the daily series, which is in turn obtained from a full
estimation of parameters and state variables using daily yield curve data.
(3) The daily data underlying these estimates were updated on 31-Dec-2021 during the New Zealand day.
